## 12. Pagination with `placeholderData`

```ts
// ✅ keepPreviousData equivalent in v5
import { keepPreviousData } from '@tanstack/react-query';

const { data, isFetching } = useQuery({
  ...userQueries.list({ page }),
  placeholderData: keepPreviousData, // show stale data while new page loads
});
```

