## 13. ESLint — enforce these rules automatically

```jsonc
// .eslintrc.json
{
  "plugins": ["@tanstack/query"],
  "rules": {
    "@tanstack/query/exhaustive-deps": "error", // queryKey must include all queryFn deps
    "@tanstack/query/prefer-query-object": "error", // object signature only
    "@tanstack/query/stable-query-client": "error", // no new QueryClient in render
    "@tanstack/query/no-rest-destructuring": "warn", // rest spreads break type inference
    "@tanstack/query/no-unstable-deps": "error", // object/array literals in queryKey
  },
}
```

