## 14. File / folder convention

```
src/
  lib/
    queryClient.ts          # singleton QueryClient
  queries/
    users.queries.ts        # queryOptions + infiniteQueryOptions per domain
    posts.queries.ts
  mutations/
    users.mutations.ts      # mutationOptions per domain
  hooks/
    useCreateUser.ts        # custom hooks only when they add logic
    useUserProfile.ts
```

