## Anti-patterns cheat sheet

| ❌ Don't                                  | ✅ Do instead                                           |
| ----------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| `useQuery(key, fn, opts)` positional args | `useQuery({ queryKey, queryFn, ...opts })`              |
| `onSuccess` / `onError` on `useQuery`     | `useEffect` watching `data`, or `useMutation` callbacks |
| `isLoading` for "no data yet"             | `isPending`                                             |
| `keepPreviousData: true`                  | `placeholderData: keepPreviousData`                     |
| `new QueryClient()` in component          | module-level singleton                                  |
| Duplicated query keys across files        | `queryOptions()` factory in `*.queries.ts`              |
| Anonymous `queryFn: async () => {}`       | Named function reference from `api.ts`                  |
| `suspense: true` flag on `useQuery`       | `useSuspenseQuery`                                      |
| `enabled` on `useSuspenseQuery`           | Component composition — render child conditionally      |
